WEBVTT

00:11.920 --> 00:15.000
[Alba] <i>In life,</i>
<i>there are always decisions to be made.</i>

00:18.560 --> 00:21.880
<i>Sometimes,</i>
<i>they are small and insignificant.</i>

00:22.800 --> 00:23.960
Carlos, I...

00:24.040 --> 00:27.760
<i>At other times, they are huge</i>
<i>and can change everything forever.</i>

00:30.960 --> 00:35.400
<i>A yes or a no could mean</i>
<i>a life full of happiness or disgrace.</i>

00:36.960 --> 00:38.200
I wasn't expecting this.

00:40.320 --> 00:41.440
Is that a yes?

00:45.280 --> 00:46.600
Is that a yes?

00:51.120 --> 00:52.120
[softly] Yes.

00:53.080 --> 00:54.120
Yes.

01:00.840 --> 01:02.720
<i>Because when you can't have everything,</i>

01:04.120 --> 01:05.680
<i>you have to choose.</i>

01:06.600 --> 01:07.800
<i>And when you choose,</i>

01:09.000 --> 01:11.280
<i>there's always the fear</i>
<i>that you'll make a mistake.</i>

01:11.760 --> 01:13.400
<i>♪ I wanted love the most ♪</i>

01:13.480 --> 01:15.920
A NETFLIX ORIGINAL SERIES

01:16.000 --> 01:18.400
<i>♪ But it never stays long ♪</i>

01:19.720 --> 01:26.520
<i>♪ A notch to my bedpost</i>
<i>Pretend they're mine ♪</i>

01:27.640 --> 01:31.600
<i>♪ Sundress wrinkled on the floor</i>
<i>I'm naked, you're not here no more ♪</i>

01:31.680 --> 01:34.360
<i>♪ To keep me warm, keep me warm ♪</i>

01:35.720 --> 01:39.280
<i>♪ Crack the door with a trash bin</i>
<i>Maybe you will come back in ♪</i>

01:39.360 --> 01:42.560
<i>♪ And keep me warm, keep me warm ♪</i>

01:43.840 --> 01:48.360
<i>♪ My love, my love, my love ♪</i>

01:49.000 --> 01:55.080
<i>♪ Pour salt in the wound ♪</i>

01:55.920 --> 02:00.240
<i>♪ My love, my love, my love ♪</i>

02:00.800 --> 02:06.520
<i>♪ Pour salt in the wound ♪</i>

02:08.000 --> 02:14.074
